From 89a10ae22674dbff78cfd0d7abf891a81bde9234 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: kimchaily <ly.kimchai@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 12 Jun 2026 07:49:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add create/append anything popups (a/n keyboard shortcuts)

The 'a' (append element) and 'n' (create element) popup menus are
provided by the separate bpmn-js-create-append-anything module and
were not part of the bundled plain bpmn-js Modeler. Register the
module and bump bpmn-js within ^18 to satisfy its diagram-js >= 15.3
peer requirement.
